>166号）、五官科医院（南城河路12号）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:32px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">2.3招标内容：北区污水处理站管道流量计、污泥泵</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">更换</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、五官科医院污水处理站曝气机</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">维修、增加流量计</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">等</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:32px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">2.4发包方式：包工包料。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:32px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 32px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">投标人营业执照经营范围包含污水处理或机电设备安装等相关内容的独立法人资格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;text-indent: 32px;padding: 0;line-height: 32px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">4、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p><p style=\