供的工程量清单。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.4发包方式：包工包料。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3、投标人资格要求</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.1投标人须具有有效的机电安装工程专业承包二级及以上资质；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.2投标人须具有有效的建筑智能化工程专业承包三级及以上资质，或建筑智能化工程设计与施工二级及以上资质；</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.3投标人须具有有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.4拟派的项目经理必须具有贰级及以注册建造师证（专业为机电安装），并具有安全生产B类证，且从本工程投标文件递交截止之日起无在建工程。（提供项目经理建造师证书、安全生产B类证、无在建工程承诺书）。投标人需提供项目经理在本单位连续缴纳6个月及以上的社保证明（提供社保证明原件）。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路8号8楼810室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间2020年10月12日8时至2020年10月14日18时。联系人：刘永杰，0515-68037830；手机：13626222271。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5、本项目采用竞争性谈判方式。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">6、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">7、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话0515-66696810。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:20pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 18px;\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p><p style=\"background-color:#ffffff; line-height:25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:right; \"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">时间：2020年10月12日</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0pt; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2503','3327','1','','','一、盐城市儿童医院传染科病房医用气体和呼叫系统安装工程已具备招标条件，现邀请合格的潜在投标人参加本工程的投标工作。二、江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。三、项目概况3.1工程名称：盐城市儿童医院传染科病房医用气','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1601395200','<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:center; \"><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><br /><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">一、盐城市儿童医院</span><span style=\"font-family:\">传染科病房医用气体和呼叫系统安装</span><span style=\"font-family:\">工程已具备招标条件，现邀请合格的潜在投标人参加本工程的投标工作。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">二、江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司受招标人委托具体负责本项目的招标事宜。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">三、项目概况</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3.1</span><span style=\"font-family:\">工程名称：盐城市儿童医院传染科病房医用气体和呼叫系统安装工程。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:\">工程地点：盐城市毓龙西路</span><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\">号。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3.3</span><span style=\"font-family:\">招标范围：盐城市儿童医院</span><span style=\"font-family:\">传染科病房医用气体和呼叫系统</span><span style=\"font-family:\">安装</span><span style=\"font-family:\">，具体以招标人提供的设计图纸、技术要求和工程量清单为准。招标人保留对招标范围调整的权利。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3.4</span><span style=\"font-family:\">工期要求：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">25</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日历天，并满足盐城市儿童医院</span><span style=\"font-family:\">医疗</span><span style=\"font-family:\">要求。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">3.5</span><span style=\"font-family:\">质量标准：国家合格标准，并通过招标人及相关部门验收合格。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">四、投标申请人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">4.1</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">投标人资质条件：投标人须</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">同时</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">具有建设行政主管部门核发的建筑机电安装工程专业承包三级及以上资质</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">和建筑智能化三级及以上资质，</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">并取得安全生产许可证。</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">可以联合体投标。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24.1pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">投标人还须同时具有下列</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">四</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">种有效的证书：（1）《特种设备安装改造维修许可证》；（</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">2</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">）《医疗器械经营许可证》（或《医疗器械生产许可证》</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">；</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">（</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">3</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">）《医疗器械注册证（中心供氧、中心吸引系统）》。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">4.2</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">项目负责人资格要求：具有机电安装专业二级及以上注册建造师资格，并具有安全生产考核证（B类）。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">4.3</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">业绩要求：自</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">2017</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">1</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">月</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">1</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">日以来（以施工合同签订日期为准），投标人须承担过一项单项合同金额达</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">10</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">万及以上的医用气体安装等类似施工业绩（投标时须提供施工合同原件）。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">4.4</span><span style=\"font-family:\">财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:\">信誉要求：投标申请人近三年内没有被司法部门或行业管理部门查处；或虽有违反法律法规行为、被依法取消投标资格但期限已满的；或因招标投标活动中有违法违规等不良行为的、被招标投标管理部门公示限制但限制期限已满的；没有处于被责令停业、财产被接管、冻结、破产等状态。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\">项目负责人、委托代理人为投标人本单位正式职工，从投标截止日当月向前连续</span><span style=\"font-family:\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\">个月均在投标人本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如投标截止日期为</span><span style=\"font-family:\">2019</span><span style=\"font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:\">*</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日，则为</span><span style=\"font-family:\">2019</span><span style=\"font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:\">6-11</span><span style=\"font-family:\">月养老保险均在投标人本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:\">本工程施工项目经理部主要管理人员包括项目负责人、技术负责人、施工员、安全员、质量员。投标时，仅需提供项目负责人相关资料，其他现场人员在中标签订施工合同备案时按苏建建管〔</span><span style=\"font-family:\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:\">〕</span><span style=\"font-family:\">236</span><span style=\"font-family:\">号文要求配备到位。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:\">本次招标工程招标人一律不接受联合体投标报名。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">五、投标保证金：</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">本项目投标保证金为人民币</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\"> 3000 </span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">元整</span><span style=\"font-family:\">，具体交纳方式详见招标文件约定。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">六、本项目资格审查采用资格后审办法。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">七、本工程评标办法采用“</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">合理低价法</span><span style=\"background-color:#00ffff; font-family:\">”。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">八、请具备主要资格条件的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"font-family:\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日至</span><span style=\"font-family:\">2020</span><span style=\"font-family:\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:\">日（每日上午</span><span style=\"font-family:\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:\">时至</span><span style=\"font-family:\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">00</span><span style=\"font-family:\">时，下午</span><span style=\"font-family:\">14</span><span style=\"font-family:\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:\">时至</span><span style=\"font-family:\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:\">00</span><span style=\"font-family:\">时）携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，注明联系人电话及邮箱）至江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司（盐城市青年西路</span><span style=\"font-family:\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:\">05</span><span style=\"font-family:\">室）报名并领取招标文件。</span><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">地址：盐城市毓龙西路</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:\">号</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">联系人：金仁甫</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">0515-</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">66698027</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">招标代理机构：江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent:24pt; \"><span style=\"font-family:\">地址：盐城市青年西路</span><span style=\"font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">8</span><span style=\"font-family:\">号</span></p><p style=\"line-height:26.25pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:0pt; margin-right:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-indent