 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></span></p><p style=\";text-align:right;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p><p style=\";text-align:right;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时间：</span>2020年6月</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p>','','','','','');
